  "prompt": "Will the celebrities who promised to move if Trump won, really leave the US?",
  "response": "When Donald Trump was elected president in 2016, several celebrities publicly claimed they would move out of the United States if he won. However, most of these statements were made rhetorically as expressions of discontent and concern rather than literal plans. In the aftermath of the election, the majority of these celebrities did not follow through with relocating. Such declarations are often made for emphasis rather than as serious commitments. Therefore, it's unlikely that many will actually leave the country if faced with a similar situation.",
